import React from 'react'; const UserProfile = ({ user }) => { const { timestamp, name, email, image, about, education, experience, skills, projects, certifications, awards, researchPapers, } = user; return (

{name}

Email: {email}

Timestamp: {timestamp}

About Yourself

{about}

{education}

Experience

{experience}

Your Skills

    {skills.map((skill, index) => (
  • {skill}
    • ))}

Project Links

    {projects.map((project, index) => (
  • {project.title}
    • ))}

Certifications / Courses

    {certifications.map((certification, index) => (
  • {certification}
    • ))}

Awards / Achievements

    {awards.map((award, index) => (

  • {paper.title}
    • ))}
); }; export default UserProfile;
